1)create virtual environment
->python -m venv venv

2)activate virtual envrinoment
->.\venv\scripts\activate

3)to install Django
->pip install Django

4)to create project
django-admin startproject menuitems

5)open project in cmd
->cd first

6)run the project
->py manage.py runserver

**in settings.py file import(line 13) 
->import os
**in line 58 modify
->'DIRS': [os.path.join(BASE_DIR,'menuitems/templates'),],
